{"tid":2011052,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[原創遊戲] 送給媽媽的遊戲","createTime":"2020-05-10T17:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T00:11:22.000Z","uid":212578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0a035b3f7e1bc57a3d73d04dcb8d967d59f9ef","tid":2011052,"uid":212578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:53:03.000Z","msg":"我同朋友做左隻小遊戲，比各位仔囡，幫媽媽瘋狂揼骨孝順下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫媽媽安裝遊戲到手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打開遊戲，偷偷寫低你想對媽媽講既說話係封信入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再俾番部電話叫你媽媽玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提醒佢如果不幸咁撞柱，你可以幫佢揼30秒骨，咁就唔洗扣分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然已經過咗母親節，<br />\n但祝天下母親，日日都係母親節！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後,<br />\n五大訴求, 缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27cce2e2aaa56332b336c732754fd48dc4d1b066","tid":2011052,"uid":212578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T18:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b7136996fe8d14d624f9fef208491d3070f3b8","tid":2011052,"uid":306000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T18:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />期待ios"},{"pid":"8f570bcc62a5d112e383068f783b4f61637df2cb","tid":2011052,"uid":212578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91b7136996fe8d14d624f9fef208491d3070f3b8","tid":2011052,"uid":306000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T18:54:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />期待ios"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T00:11:22.000Z","msg":"Thx 巴打"}]}